<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV29">
<l>parattilumpa rattaiyāki pauvanīra ṇaikkiṭan</l>
<l>turattilummo ruttitaṉṉai vaittukanta taṉṟiyum</l>
<l>narattilumpi ṟattināta ñāṉamūrtti yāyiṉā</l>
<l>yoruttaruni ṉātutaṉmai yiṉṉateṉṉa vallarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being higher than the highest, [You] rejoiced placing a woman on [Your] chest</l>
<l>having previously lain on the bed of ocean water; apart from that,</l>
<l>You were born even among humankind. O Lord! O knowledge embodied!</l>
<l>Is anyone capable of saying that such is Your nature?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
